item.title: Changelog
item.description: Changelog # All notable changes to this project are documented in this page. The format is based on Keep a Changelog. 1.6.5-rc.1 - 2024-01-07 # Changed # Upgrades NDMF to 1.3.0-rc.1 #815 Use Title instead of Description since substation in Title is implemented Fixed # Reference to meshes will be merged is removed #808 VRM: Fix MergeSkinnedMesh breaking BlendShapeClip / VRM10Expression #810 Unknown component warning were shown multiple time for one type #818 In addition, location of the unknown components are shown on the error report.
